Feature	                                       Linear Search	                                                               Binary Search
Works on Sorted Array	                          âŒ No                                                                 	âœ… Yes, must be sorted
Speed (Time Complexity)                      	O(n) â€“ slow for large data	                                             O(log n) â€“ super fast ğŸš€
Logic	                                     Check every element one by one                                           	Divide array in half every time
